Added possibility to define `WeakInnerJoin` and `WeakLeftJoin`.
Example of usage:
```cs
var query =
	from t in table
	from j1 in forJoin.WeakInnerJoin(j1 => t.Id == j1.ParentId)
	from j2 in forJoin.WeakInnerJoin(j2 => t.Id == j1.Id)
	select new
	{
		T = t,
		J1 = j1,
		J2 = j2
	};
```
